# Scribe Cloud runs entirely on Cloudflare (Worker + static assets) — no server secrets needed.
#
# Public client config lives in public/config.json (committed; values are public / RLS-protected):
#   supabaseUrl, supabaseAnonKey (publishable key), asrUrl (HF Space — Burmese only)
#
# The Worker's Workers AI binding is declared in wrangler.jsonc ("ai": { "binding": "AI" }) and
# auto-provisions on `wrangler deploy` — there is NO API key to set.
#
# Burmese ASR = self-hosted SeamlessM4T HF Space (see hf-space/README.md). Everything else =
# Cloudflare Workers AI Whisper, handled in worker.js. Gemini and Netlify are no longer used.
